4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper may involve the use of AI techniques to detect cyber attacks or to synthesize the ABSRA-robust supervisor.
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper proposes a synthesis algorithm to ensure that the computed supervisor is ABSRA-robust, which involves software engineering techniques.
